Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.639
It is important to have visibility into your cloud resources and applications.

00:00:05.639 --> 00:00:08.129
Being able to answer questions like,

00:00:08.130 --> 00:00:10.214
how is the server performing?

00:00:10.214 --> 00:00:12.914
What is the current load on the server?

00:00:12.914 --> 00:00:17.594
What is the root cause of an application error that a user is seeing?

00:00:17.594 --> 00:00:20.714
What is the path that leads to this error?

00:00:20.714 --> 00:00:26.670
Being able to answer these questions is imperative to providing good user experiences.

00:00:26.670 --> 00:00:32.465
However, monitoring distributed systems that run in the cloud can be difficult.

00:00:32.465 --> 00:00:34.800
For applications that run in the Cloud,

00:00:34.799 --> 00:00:38.959
you will need access to logging and auditing services to

00:00:38.960 --> 00:00:44.370
help you proactively monitor your resources and applications.

